reviews.text: Ordered Blue Cheese Burger. $148 burger looked and tasted like $48 fast food burger. Patty looks factory manufactured. Fries were cold and it took long time to get my food even though restaurant was pretty empty.
Relaxing place for chill out and groups.  Be patient as not enough staff to serve.  Never go there if you don't have 3 hours for your meal

An Australian chain restaurant in Hong Kong. Service is good and food is great. The price is above average but the service is great. Their black bread loaf is famous and delicious and you can ask for refill for free.

Been avoiding outback for the last 8 years in Hong Kong as they don't know how to cook proper meat.  

Well decided to give them one last go before leaving hk and this particular venue redeemed their name. Ordered the slow cooked prime rib 16oz and loved it.

I would have given it 5 stars, but unfortunately service is equally important.  In this case there was none!  When ordering, the server said it was too early to order this item (7pm), which after told him the time he placed my order.  And after receiving the dish I couldn't get a single server to come to my table to order additional drinks until I was all done and asked for the bill.

Good food. Nice ambience. Large table for a group of 11 and we were able to hear ourselves, as there was no noisy music blaring at us. All sorts of western dishes on the menu. I went for the cheeseburger and found it delightful. The portion seemed a bit small though. I suppose it's the "typical" HKer portion. They don't eat much like the "typical" Americans or Aussies (pardon the stereotyping... But you get what I mean 😉.)

reviews.text: 😋牛扒好味👍

地方坐得舒適，不限時任坐，感覺良好。
食物味道平穩，沒有難食但也沒有特別好食。
以環境、食物計，下午茶餐性價比高

外面的封面圖片精美，望落好好食，但係千祈唔好俾佢嘅外表而矇騙咗，嗰晚我同我家人慶祝生日，嗌咗個set，其他配菜味道十分麻麻地，而咁多種配菜入邊最好食嘅應該就係嗰個是日餐湯and長腳蟹，而令我最失望最失望嘅就係佢嘅扒，又硬又無肉汁又hai，我家人更話似食緊樹皮or鞋底，不過而家餐廳亦有佢嘅優點，當時我同我家人食緊塊扒嘅時候一直都喺度暗啞底批評塊扒，可能個waiter聽到我哋批評塊扒，跟住佢就走埋嚟問我哋食物如何，我家人就非常直白噉同佢講話又硬又唔Juicy又hai，佢更十分耐心地聽我哋批評，呢個態度實在加分👍(如果唔係因為佢呢個態度我可能連一粒星都唔會俾)佢更幫我哋更換咗新嘅一份扒，but……都係好hai😂，實在令我有啲失望，我家人話超級失望(因為佢本來抱好大期望嘅😂)，以上就係小妹嘅小小意見，如果大家想去嘅話仍然可以去，但小妹在此建議大家不要抱太大期望😂

Ordered Blue Cheese Burger. $148 burger looked and tasted like $48 fast food burger. Patty looks factory manufactured. Fries were cold and it took long time to get my food even though restaurant was pretty empty.
開了好耐，奧海城第一次食，座位算舒適。服務有禮，但好似人手不足，加水refill 等要主動叫。牛柳足料，冇渣，夠軟熟。其他ok la。意粉也夠味。

reviews.text: A nice shopping mall with lots of good choice of food, there is a theater there too
Great collection but feel like most outlets here are quite pricey.

A lovely place for families, friends and couples, many spots for activities, watch movies, have meals, and get everything you want with different styles of shops. Also, it has exhibitions most of the time, featuring different themes and brands, can spend the whole afternoon till the night

Overall neat, tidy and with moderate variety of shops.

The time limited events are excellent, be sure to check their Facebook pages for details.
Great place for food and shopping , can find high quality or less expensive upon individual named
